\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\">&nbsp;国家在今年依然延续对瓷砖生产的严厉监控，下面哈德逊小编原创</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\">图解<font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2015</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">最新</font></span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\">国家瓷砖分类检验标准。</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align:left; \\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\">&nbsp;<img width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"750\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-03-25/f97fedd3e93f75b40b57398603cfc8e3.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"图解2015国家瓷砖分类检验标准.jpg\\\\\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align:left; \\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\">&nbsp;广东</span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); text-decoration: underline;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"15\\\\\">哈德逊瓷砖</span></span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\\\''; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; \\\\\">严格遵守国家瓷砖分类检验标准，严于律己，生产的瓷砖产品均在国家标准之上，力求为广大消费者提供远超国家瓷砖分类检验标准的瓷砖优等品。除此之外，哈德逊瓷砖做到传承国外大品牌对瓷砖的分类检验标准，产品质量上乘。如此高质产品，除了在国内热销，还远销海外，深受海内外消费者厚爱。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align:left; \\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun:\\\\''yes\\